data.description: Lovely 1.5-story split-floorplan home lives like a ranch with a bonus room upstairs on over an acre! Spacious, updated kitchen with new granite, tile backsplash and new flooring opens to the breakfast area and large family room. Large Family room has 2 ceiling fans and gas burning, stone fireplace. Dining Room is on the front of the house and overlooks the beautifully landscaped front yard. Master bedroom with huge walk-in closet and master bath; with access to the screened porch. On the other side of the house are 2 secondary bedrooms and a fully renovated hall bath with walk-in shower. Large deck and screened porch overlook the wooded, fenced backyard and are perfect for entertaining! Large Bonus room could be used as an office, playroom, guest area, or flex space. Two unfinished areas upstairs are ideal for storage and/or has potential to be finished for additional bath and/or office/flex space. Tons of potential with this spacious house!! Conveniently located just off highway 42 and within 5 minutes of highway 70; and less than 20 minutes to I40 and I95!!
